### 1. **markerStyleToMarker 関数の定義（2箇所で独立定義）**

#### `/root/flowmaid/src/store/useFlowStore.ts` (行20-31)
```typescript
function markerStyleToMarker(style?: MarkerStyle, color?: string) {
  switch (style) {
    case "arrow":
      return { type: MarkerType.Arrow, color };
    case "arrowclosed":
      return { type: MarkerType.ArrowClosed, color };
    case "none":
      return undefined;
    default:
      return undefined;
  }
}
```
**特徴**: `color`パラメータを受け取り、Markerオブジェクトに付与可能

#### `/root/flowmaid/src/lib/component-children.ts` (行13-24)
```typescript
